Ballistic Overkill basic cheat. This is kind of old, it might not be fully working anymore.

More info over here: https://www.unknowncheats.me/forum/other-fps-games/205806-ballistic-overkill.html

About the projects:

/BallisticOverkill.csproj - The actual cheat.
/LoaderDll.vcxproj        - The loader dll. This must be injected on the process.
/LoaderLoader.vcxproj     - A simple injector for the loader dll.


